(188, 1, '', 0, '', '0', 'Hoàn Tất Bảo Trì - Gộp Server', 'hoan-tat-bao-tri-gop-server', '<p><strong>&nbsp;Th&acirc;n ch&agrave;o qu&yacute; bằng hữu !</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong><img alt="" src="/static/uploads/editor/C%E1%BB%A5m%20M%C3%A1y%20Ch%E1%BB%A7%20S%C6%A1n/Nguy%E1%BB%87t%20S%C6%A1n/truymong.jpg" style="height:400px; width:540px" /></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;Sau 2 ti&ecirc;́ng, BQT đã&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 0)">G&ocirc;̣p 4 Cụm máy chủ Truy M&ocirc;̣ng &nbsp;thành c&ocirc;ng</span>&nbsp;- chúc quý bằng hữu có những gi&acirc;y phút trải nghi&ecirc;̣m game th&acirc;̣t vui vẻ và có những tr&acirc;̣n pk lớn với những thành vi&ecirc;n mới của 4 Cụm máy chủ g&ocirc;̣p lại nhé.</strong></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:18px"><strong><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 0)">M&aacute;y Chủ&nbsp;Ho&agrave;n Tất Bảo Tr&igrave;</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color:rgb(255, 0, 0)"><u>Code Hằng Sơn + Nam Giang :</u></span></span>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:22px">[ </span><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color:#FF0000">GCDB345C</span></span><span style="font-size:22px">&nbsp;]</span></strong></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color:rgb(255, 0, 0)"><u>Code Phật Sơn + Tuyết Sơn&nbsp;:</u>&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#FFFF00">v&igrave; l&yacute; do kỹ thuật n&ecirc;n sẽ c&oacute; v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 25/3 nh&eacute;</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Hi&ecirc;̣n tại đang có&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 0)">Event Khuy&ecirc;́n mãi 100% b&acirc;́t kì m&ecirc;̣nh giá&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>- T